  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for glibc",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for glibc fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-5928: libio: Fix ungetwc operating on byte stream (bsc#1262464, BZ #33998)\n- CVE-2026-5450: stdio-common: Fix buffer overflow in scanf %mc (bsc#1262465, BZ #34008)\n- CVE-2026-4046: Use pending character state in IBM1390, IBM1399 character sets (bsc#1261206, BZ #33980)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
